WEBVTT

00:20.060 --> 00:21.460
It happened so suddenly.

00:21.480 --> 00:22.680
We were not prepared,

00:24.230 --> 00:26.090
so we had to bury Master like this.

00:26.830 --> 00:29.630
Ever since he took the poison
given by His Majesty,

00:30.350 --> 00:31.810
he had been terminally ill

00:32.200 --> 00:34.110
and lost all his martial arts skills.

00:34.110 --> 00:36.670
And with this surge of anger,
he passed away.

00:42.880 --> 00:44.210
Master has passed away.

00:44.670 --> 00:45.470
Young Master,

00:45.920 --> 00:47.750
whether you stay or go,

00:48.920 --> 00:50.650
no one will interfere anymore.

01:02.880 --> 01:04.150
Just as you said,

01:04.840 --> 01:05.590
Master...

01:06.790 --> 01:07.680
had no choice.

02:49.630 --> 02:54.900
[REBIRTH]

02:55.350 --> 02:57.829
[Episode 33]

03:01.690 --> 03:04.030
[In Memory of My Grandfather,
Zhuge Muqing]

03:04.960 --> 03:05.760
Young Master!

03:11.750 --> 03:12.750
It's really you.

03:29.310 --> 03:30.520
You really are alive.

03:35.400 --> 03:35.910
Yue Da,

03:36.520 --> 03:37.560
after I left,

03:38.150 --> 03:39.280
have you been well?

03:40.910 --> 03:41.710
Young Master.

03:43.190 --> 03:44.079
We...

03:45.150 --> 03:46.550
we've all been very well.

03:47.430 --> 03:48.079
Yue Liu,

03:51.870 --> 03:53.329
you are terrible at lying.

03:56.400 --> 03:57.200
Young Master,

03:58.000 --> 03:59.660
please leave Qingshan Manor.

03:59.840 --> 04:00.900
As the Moon Guards,

04:01.360 --> 04:02.960
we have accepted our fate

04:03.120 --> 04:05.240
the moment we entered Qingshan Manor.

04:05.240 --> 04:07.280
We have to be responsible for our choices.

04:07.280 --> 04:08.080
Young Master,

04:08.280 --> 04:09.540
please go your own way.

04:09.750 --> 04:11.030
You don't have to stay for us.

04:11.030 --> 04:12.840
Please leave.

04:14.030 --> 04:16.690
Young Master!
You cannot leave Qingshan Manor!

04:17.390 --> 04:19.040
The Master is dead!

04:19.310 --> 04:20.390
Let go of me!

04:21.120 --> 04:21.920
Young Master,

04:22.430 --> 04:24.240
you have become King Ximeng.

04:24.560 --> 04:25.430
Qingshan Manor

04:25.680 --> 04:28.560
will fall into the hands
of the third branch of the Zhuge family.

04:28.560 --> 04:30.310
Their master, Zhuge Xi,

04:30.870 --> 04:32.950
was beaten to death by Chu Qiao.

04:33.510 --> 04:35.630
The third branch hates you to the core.

04:35.630 --> 04:37.240
If we Moon Guards stay here,

04:37.310 --> 04:38.750
death would be a mercy.

04:38.890 --> 04:39.730
I'm afraid by then,

04:39.730 --> 04:41.800
we will be tortured to the point
where we'd rather be dead!

04:41.800 --> 04:42.950
The Master is gone,

04:44.000 --> 04:45.860
but Qingshan Manor is still here!

04:46.360 --> 04:47.000
Yue Ming,

04:47.800 --> 04:49.460
you fled without permission.

04:49.560 --> 04:51.190
According to the rules of Qingshan Manor,
you will be executed!

04:51.190 --> 04:51.720
Yes!

04:52.060 --> 04:52.990
-Go!
-Let him go!

04:55.240 --> 04:56.040
Young Master,

04:56.560 --> 04:58.490
this is the rule of Qingshan Manor.

05:11.950 --> 05:12.680
Zhan Fu.

05:15.120 --> 05:17.450
I will return to Zhenhuangcheng with you.

05:18.680 --> 05:19.800
Qingshan Manor

05:20.600 --> 05:22.660
will not be given to the third branch.

05:24.070 --> 05:25.950
Welcome back, Young Master!

05:25.950 --> 05:27.720
Welcome back, Young Master!

05:27.720 --> 05:29.480
Welcome back, Young Master!

05:29.600 --> 05:31.390
Welcome back, Young Master!

05:42.310 --> 05:42.950
Hurry!

05:47.190 --> 05:48.560
This is the military camp of Ximeng.

05:48.560 --> 05:50.360
Please leave, King of Great Yan.

05:54.190 --> 05:55.590
He Xiao, look carefully.

05:55.920 --> 05:57.040
I am unarmed now.

05:57.270 --> 05:58.600
You can kill me anytime.

05:59.040 --> 06:00.770
But I will not leave Chu's side

06:02.000 --> 06:03.160
until she wakes up.

06:04.680 --> 06:05.310
Chu.

06:05.830 --> 06:06.750
Chu, hang on.

06:07.160 --> 06:09.270
She fainted from losing too much blood.

06:09.270 --> 06:09.920
Chu.

06:10.820 --> 06:11.800
You'll be fine.

06:12.870 --> 06:13.600
Chu.

06:32.870 --> 06:33.800
How is she?

06:34.360 --> 06:36.020
The wounds have been treated.

06:38.800 --> 06:40.200
But Chu still has a fever.

06:40.430 --> 06:42.090
Lady Chu has two knife wounds.

06:42.480 --> 06:43.870
Although they are not fatal,

06:43.870 --> 06:45.130
she lost a lot of blood.

06:45.190 --> 06:47.720
It is normal that she won't wake up
for a while.

06:47.720 --> 06:49.390
We just need to take turns
watching her here.

06:49.390 --> 06:53.050
She will be fine once she safely
gets through these couple of days.

08:04.800 --> 08:06.130
What are you doing here?

08:07.160 --> 08:07.920
Tell me!

08:15.630 --> 08:18.960
What right do you have
to come to the military camp to see Chu?

08:21.240 --> 08:23.120
If it weren't for you and Zhuge Muqing,

08:23.120 --> 08:24.850
she wouldn't be hurt like this!

08:31.040 --> 08:32.770
There are wounds on her left arm

08:33.440 --> 08:34.320
and abdomen.

08:35.360 --> 08:36.890
Although they are not deep,

08:37.000 --> 08:39.390
they were caused
by Qingshan Manor's glazed iron.

08:39.390 --> 08:41.320
Even if her meridians are not hurt,

08:41.600 --> 08:42.799
they are hard to heal.

08:46.360 --> 08:47.320
Have Xiao Ran

08:48.120 --> 08:50.790
make some medicinal wine
with Yinlin snake blood and Huaying grass.

08:50.790 --> 08:52.150
It can remove putrefaction
and promote tissue regeneration.

08:52.150 --> 08:53.120
In 2 days,

08:53.870 --> 08:54.790
she will wake up.

08:54.790 --> 08:56.720
How do you know the details so well?

09:00.200 --> 09:02.200
I thought I was the one who saved Chu.

09:02.550 --> 09:04.870
It seems I was one step behind you again.

09:05.240 --> 09:06.900
Today in the Yong Army's camp,

09:08.390 --> 09:10.250
you offered yourself as the price

09:10.630 --> 09:13.560
in exchange for Zhuge Muqing
to release them, right?

09:14.480 --> 09:15.540
Tomorrow morning,

09:16.360 --> 09:19.440
I will leave with my grandfather
and the people of Qingshan Manor.

09:19.440 --> 09:21.240
The Yong Army will still be here,

09:21.790 --> 09:23.190
but without a commander,

09:23.600 --> 09:26.320
they won't do anything to Ximeng
anytime soon.

09:28.910 --> 09:30.510
Ever since I've known you,

09:31.750 --> 09:34.150
you have always been this self-righteous,

09:34.360 --> 09:36.750
thinking you bear the burden
of the country

09:36.750 --> 09:38.000
and its people.

09:39.600 --> 09:41.270
But you are just a mortal too.

09:41.720 --> 09:43.670
I don't care what promises

09:43.750 --> 09:44.960
or deals you have made.

09:44.960 --> 09:46.620
Zhuge Muqing is already dead.

09:47.120 --> 09:48.360
You should stay

09:48.360 --> 09:51.000
and help Chu through this.

09:57.240 --> 09:58.040
In this world,

09:58.960 --> 09:59.720
not everyone

09:59.720 --> 10:01.480
can follow their heart

10:02.000 --> 10:03.730
and do whatever they want to do.

10:04.240 --> 10:05.600
We grew up together

10:05.870 --> 10:07.670
and understand each other best.

10:08.670 --> 10:09.750
I have my reasons.

10:12.030 --> 10:12.960
Before I return,

10:13.720 --> 10:15.320
take good care of Xing for me.

10:17.480 --> 10:18.270
Zhuge Yue,

10:19.270 --> 10:21.440
I don't understand you anymore.

10:21.840 --> 10:24.170
And you didn't treat Chu like this before.

10:26.080 --> 10:27.210
-Bravo!
-Good shot!

10:40.670 --> 10:41.910
Bravo!

10:43.150 --> 10:43.750
Thanks!

10:54.910 --> 10:55.670
Zhuge Yue.

10:56.120 --> 10:57.750
I've taken a liking
to a maid in your manor.

10:57.750 --> 10:59.280
How about you give her to me?

10:59.630 --> 11:02.270
I will certainly grant what you ask,
Your Highness.

11:02.270 --> 11:03.360
But which branch

11:03.360 --> 11:04.870
does she belong to?

11:05.670 --> 11:07.480
She said she's from the Nonexistent Yard,

11:07.480 --> 11:08.740
and her name is Nobody.

11:09.000 --> 11:11.130
She makes clay figures under Mrs. Dou.

11:13.600 --> 11:15.320
There is no such person in Qingshan Manor.

11:15.320 --> 11:16.180
How can that be?

11:16.390 --> 11:17.450
Her name is Nobody,

11:17.510 --> 11:18.630
and she's from the Nonexistent Yard,

11:18.630 --> 11:21.270
making clay figures under Mrs. Dou.

11:21.390 --> 11:23.080
Doesn't that mean she doesn't exist?

11:23.080 --> 11:24.480
She was messing with you.

11:25.240 --> 11:28.320
How dare she lie to me?

11:28.960 --> 11:29.890
I'll go find her.

11:33.630 --> 11:35.240
Nobody from the Nonexistent Yard?

11:35.240 --> 11:36.440
I can't believe she came up with that.

11:36.440 --> 11:37.120
Zhuge Yue,

11:37.550 --> 11:40.210
this Xing in your courtyard
has quite the nerve.

11:40.240 --> 11:41.910
She even dared to lie to a prince.

11:41.910 --> 11:42.630
I like her.

11:43.000 --> 11:44.000
She's too bold.

11:44.270 --> 11:45.550
She needs strict discipline.

11:45.550 --> 11:46.440
No need for that.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.500
Just give her to me.

11:48.150 --> 11:49.270
If you keep disciplining her,

11:49.270 --> 11:49.750
she will turn into

11:49.750 --> 11:51.440
a block of ice like you.

11:53.960 --> 11:54.550
No.

11:55.240 --> 11:56.300
If I give her to you,

11:56.390 --> 11:58.510
the Thirteenth Prince
will definitely fall out with me.

11:58.510 --> 11:59.840
Pick another maid.

12:01.200 --> 12:01.790
Wait.

12:03.150 --> 12:03.910
Zhuge Yue.

12:04.720 --> 12:06.000
We grew up together.

12:06.510 --> 12:08.570
I've never seen you afraid of anyone.

12:10.510 --> 12:11.750
Could it be

12:12.240 --> 12:13.910
that you can't bear to part with her

12:13.910 --> 12:15.710
and want to keep her by your side?

12:21.630 --> 12:22.440
Zhuge Yue!

12:30.240 --> 12:31.000
Yan Xun,

12:32.320 --> 12:34.120
I will trust you one last time.

12:34.750 --> 12:36.010
Take good care of Xing.

12:37.030 --> 12:38.840
Keep her safe

12:40.720 --> 12:41.630
until I return.

13:48.440 --> 13:49.030
Xing.

13:50.200 --> 13:52.510
Since the establishment
of the new government in Ximeng,

13:52.510 --> 13:54.320
crises have been emerging everywhere.

13:54.320 --> 13:57.120
You and I have faced death together
several times.

13:57.320 --> 13:59.380
We should face the enemy side by side.

14:00.080 --> 14:02.140
But my identity has now been exposed.

14:02.670 --> 14:05.550
The bloody conflicts in both lands
all stem from this.

14:05.550 --> 14:07.390
With my grandfather's sudden passing,

14:07.390 --> 14:08.870
the wolves in Great Yong who are in power

14:08.870 --> 14:11.070
will only grow more covetous of Ximeng.

14:11.510 --> 14:12.440
On this journey,

14:12.840 --> 14:15.500
I must first quell the unrest
in Qingshan Manor,

14:15.910 --> 14:18.770
then eradicate
the deep-rooted ills of Great Yong.

14:19.630 --> 14:21.960
Only then can Ximeng enjoy lasting peace.

14:22.390 --> 14:23.360
Upon my return,

14:24.030 --> 14:25.230
I will keep my promise

14:26.390 --> 14:27.590
and reunite with you.

14:48.440 --> 14:49.500
Chu, you're awake.

14:52.440 --> 14:53.670
And your fever is gone.

14:53.670 --> 14:54.930
You should be fine now.

14:57.600 --> 14:59.030
Lady Chu, please calm down.

14:59.030 --> 15:00.080
You've been unconscious for days.

15:00.080 --> 15:01.270
Your body is very weak.

15:01.270 --> 15:02.800
I'll ask Minglu to help you.

15:08.550 --> 15:09.480
Where is Minglu?

15:15.030 --> 15:16.440
What exactly happened?

15:25.360 --> 15:26.600
Before Minglu left,

15:28.960 --> 15:30.160
did she say anything?

15:31.150 --> 15:32.430
She said nothing.

15:33.270 --> 15:36.270
She stopped breathing
just as she arrived at the camp.

15:36.670 --> 15:38.670
Except for these two pieces of clothing,

15:38.670 --> 15:40.080
she left nothing behind.

16:00.510 --> 16:01.390
Impossible.

16:03.440 --> 16:04.670
She can't be dead.

16:06.270 --> 16:07.270
It's impossible.

16:09.320 --> 16:10.150
I'll go find her!

16:10.150 --> 16:10.720
Chu!

16:10.720 --> 16:12.390
I'll go find her! Let me go!

16:12.390 --> 16:13.120
Minglu is already dead.

16:13.120 --> 16:13.720
I'm going to find Minglu!

16:13.720 --> 16:14.510
She's already dead!

16:14.510 --> 16:15.600
She's not dead!

16:15.600 --> 16:17.000
-She's dead!
-She's not!

16:19.480 --> 16:21.200
Minglu is not dead!

16:22.480 --> 16:24.080
She's not dead!

16:25.960 --> 16:27.120
Minglu...

16:28.480 --> 16:31.150
Minglu died for me.

16:34.870 --> 16:36.240
Minglu...

16:39.000 --> 16:39.960
I'm sorry.

16:42.120 --> 16:44.630
I'm sorry, Minglu!

16:44.790 --> 16:46.150
Minglu!

16:53.030 --> 16:54.390
Minglu!

17:23.109 --> 17:24.550
I saw him that night.

17:25.510 --> 17:27.040
I wanted to ask him clearly,

17:27.510 --> 17:29.110
but when I caught up with him,

17:29.310 --> 17:30.440
he had already left.

17:35.240 --> 17:36.640
He only left this behind.

17:41.350 --> 17:42.350
Zhuge Yue said

17:43.240 --> 17:44.720
he wouldn't leave me
without saying goodbye.

17:44.720 --> 17:46.160
He has made his choice.

17:46.790 --> 17:48.400
Don't you understand?

17:49.200 --> 17:50.790
What is that supposed to mean?

17:50.790 --> 17:53.390
He was born into the Zhuge family
of Great Yong.

17:53.590 --> 17:54.640
Zhuge Muqing

17:55.000 --> 17:56.720
had always treated him
as the heir to Qingshan Manor.

17:56.720 --> 17:57.400
Yan Xun.

17:58.760 --> 18:00.690
What exactly are you trying to say?

18:03.070 --> 18:04.590
He is different from us.

18:04.830 --> 18:06.070
We don't have family,

18:06.070 --> 18:06.920
but he does.

18:07.240 --> 18:08.830
Qingshan Manor is his home.

18:08.960 --> 18:10.750
Zhuge Muqing is his family.

18:11.000 --> 18:12.270
Even if he can momentarily

18:12.270 --> 18:13.440
give up his family and Great Yong

18:13.440 --> 18:14.310
for you,

18:14.480 --> 18:16.010
can he really do it forever?

18:16.200 --> 18:17.830
Would his family allow him to do so?

18:17.830 --> 18:19.090
No matter what you say,

18:19.880 --> 18:21.070
I believe him.

18:21.070 --> 18:21.960
You believe him?

18:21.960 --> 18:23.070
Is he worthy of your trust?

18:23.070 --> 18:24.200
Zhuge Muqing came to Ximengcheng before.

18:24.200 --> 18:25.600
Did he ever tell you that?

18:26.070 --> 18:28.310
Zhuge Muqing came to Ximengcheng
to look for him?

18:28.310 --> 18:29.880
He and I grew up together.

18:30.310 --> 18:31.570
We were like brothers.

18:31.680 --> 18:33.280
I know him better than you do.

18:33.510 --> 18:34.840
Born in the Zhuge family

18:35.350 --> 18:36.790
and bearing the responsibility
of Qingshan Manor,

18:36.790 --> 18:38.920
he has many things beyond his control.

18:40.110 --> 18:41.110
For so many years,

18:41.510 --> 18:42.720
at critical moments,

18:43.400 --> 18:45.530
he would always abandon what he wanted

18:46.070 --> 18:47.960
and make the advantageous choice.

18:47.960 --> 18:51.270
Just like when he chose to stand
by the Emperor of Great Yong

18:51.750 --> 18:53.270
and watch the entire Yan family perish.

18:53.270 --> 18:54.200
Enough, Yan Xun!

18:58.830 --> 18:59.550
I'm tired.

19:00.880 --> 19:02.940
I don't want to listen to you anymore.

19:04.830 --> 19:05.640
Fine.

19:07.070 --> 19:08.400
If you don't believe me,

19:08.680 --> 19:10.080
I'll take you to find him.

19:11.990 --> 19:14.170
[Capital of Great Yan]

19:37.270 --> 19:38.110
My Lady!

19:38.110 --> 19:38.750
Bad news!

19:38.750 --> 19:40.240
The elder of Lanchuan Tribe has rebelled!

19:40.240 --> 19:41.000
As we speak,

19:41.000 --> 19:42.790
the Lanchuan cavalry
has already reached Lexian!

19:42.790 --> 19:44.030
Let's hurry out and hide somewhere!

19:44.030 --> 19:44.640
What?

19:45.110 --> 19:46.830
Why did the elder of Lanchuan Tribe rebel?

19:46.830 --> 19:47.630
I have no idea.

19:48.200 --> 19:50.440
But the nobles in the Capital of Great Yan
who heard the news

19:50.440 --> 19:51.640
have all fled.

19:51.640 --> 19:53.000
The Lanchuan Tribe and the Pale Tribe

19:53.000 --> 19:55.400
have always had ulterior motives
toward Yan Xun.

19:55.400 --> 19:56.310
This time they were forced

19:56.310 --> 19:57.720
to show their full hand.

19:59.590 --> 20:00.070
It must be...

20:00.070 --> 20:00.720
Your Highness,

20:00.720 --> 20:02.070
don't worry about this for now.

20:02.070 --> 20:03.590
His Majesty is not in Great Yan now.

20:03.590 --> 20:05.110
There are hardly
any Black Eagle Army soldiers left

20:05.110 --> 20:05.960
stationed in the Capital of Great Yan.

20:05.960 --> 20:07.310
If the Lanchuan cavalry
reaches the city gate,

20:07.310 --> 20:08.270
we'll be in trouble.

20:08.270 --> 20:08.910
Your Highness,

20:08.910 --> 20:09.910
let's go now!

20:21.880 --> 20:23.880
Search the whole city
for Yan Xun's remnants!

20:23.880 --> 20:24.960
Kill them all!

20:25.440 --> 20:26.030
Yes!

20:34.880 --> 20:35.830
What happened?

21:05.640 --> 21:06.440
Are you okay?

21:08.400 --> 21:08.920
Su?

21:11.450 --> 21:13.300
Su! Su!

21:27.480 --> 21:29.480
Su!

21:39.400 --> 21:40.400
You guys, go over there!

21:40.400 --> 21:41.460
-Hurry!
-Let's go!

21:42.920 --> 21:43.850
Check over here!

21:44.400 --> 21:44.880
Yes!

22:05.960 --> 22:06.440
Come.

22:41.070 --> 22:42.000
Why are you here?

22:45.720 --> 22:47.350
Something happened at the military camp
in the Capital of Great Yan too?

22:47.350 --> 22:49.550
Spies from the Lanchuan Tribe

22:49.550 --> 22:51.080
have infiltrated the camp.

22:51.270 --> 22:53.150
They tried to kill me
before breaching the city.

22:53.150 --> 22:54.350
I barely escaped.

22:55.000 --> 22:56.270
But don't worry.

22:56.400 --> 22:58.110
I've sent people to Yanming Pass

22:58.110 --> 22:59.440
to inform General Huan.

22:59.440 --> 23:01.240
They should have arrived by now.

23:01.590 --> 23:03.030
From Yanming Pass
to the Capital of Great Yan,

23:03.030 --> 23:04.890
it takes at least a day and a night.

23:06.110 --> 23:07.350
The cavalry of the Lanchuan Tribe

23:07.350 --> 23:08.720
has already occupied the palace.

23:08.720 --> 23:09.550
Now their people are everywhere

23:09.550 --> 23:11.080
in the Capital of Great Yan.

23:11.310 --> 23:12.310
What should we do?

23:12.590 --> 23:13.320
Don't worry.

23:14.240 --> 23:15.790
They are busy burning and looting

23:15.790 --> 23:17.830
and have no time
to deal with us for the moment.

23:17.830 --> 23:19.890
You are His Majesty's Chief General,

23:20.000 --> 23:21.130
and I am his Consort.

23:22.480 --> 23:24.240
Elder Lanchuan
hates His Majesty to the core.

23:24.240 --> 23:25.270
I'm afraid the first thing he'll do

23:25.270 --> 23:27.270
is kill us to boost their troops' morale.

23:27.270 --> 23:28.310
Hide here for now.

23:29.270 --> 23:31.800
I'll go and see
if there's a way out of the city.

23:32.430 --> 23:33.200
Cheng Yuan!

23:38.880 --> 23:39.610
Don't worry.

23:40.510 --> 23:41.480
It's safe here.

23:53.920 --> 23:54.980
Let's go together.

24:01.000 --> 24:02.030
You guys! Go over there!

24:02.030 --> 24:02.560
Let's go!

24:03.400 --> 24:03.880
Hurry!

24:12.550 --> 24:13.680
They are over there!

24:20.510 --> 24:22.160
My Lady! General Cheng!

24:22.640 --> 24:24.640
We are here to escort you as ordered!

24:25.070 --> 24:26.800
They are from the Snowy Region!

24:47.960 --> 24:49.480
My Lady, General Cheng.

24:49.790 --> 24:51.510
Thank you for your help, General Huan.

24:51.510 --> 24:53.440
Thankfullly, you arrived in time,

24:53.510 --> 24:55.400
so General Cheng and I are safe.

24:57.030 --> 24:57.750
General,

24:57.750 --> 24:59.240
the rebels of Lanchuan Tribe
have been captured.

24:59.240 --> 25:00.790
Elder Lanchuan has escaped from
the Capital of Great Yan.

25:00.790 --> 25:02.520
We have sent men to capture him.

25:02.550 --> 25:04.030
Okay, I got it.

25:04.640 --> 25:05.440
General Huan.

25:05.680 --> 25:07.010
There is one more thing.

25:07.160 --> 25:09.620
Among the captured rebels,
a small group...

25:10.590 --> 25:12.720
are cavalrymen from the Helian Tribe.

25:28.590 --> 25:29.550
Search carefully!

25:29.550 --> 25:31.160
Detain everyone in the mansion!

25:31.160 --> 25:31.790
Yes!

25:39.350 --> 25:39.880
Go!

25:46.680 --> 25:47.480
What's wrong?

25:47.790 --> 25:48.990
What is going on here?

25:51.310 --> 25:52.110
General Huan?

25:53.160 --> 25:54.240
In the middle of the night,

25:54.240 --> 25:56.440
you brought so many people to my mansion

25:56.590 --> 25:58.320
and disturbed my sweet dreams.

25:58.350 --> 25:59.480
What are you trying to do?

25:59.480 --> 26:01.110
The Lanchuan Tribe rebelled

26:01.680 --> 26:03.480
and has been burning, killing,
and looting in the capital,

26:03.480 --> 26:05.160
ruining ordinary people's families.

26:05.160 --> 26:07.400
It's a wonder you could still sleep
so soundly

26:07.400 --> 26:08.880
and dream sweet dreams.

26:09.200 --> 26:10.860
The Lanchuan Tribe rebelled?

26:11.000 --> 26:12.960
How dare they?

26:12.960 --> 26:15.110
Is the situation in the city
under control now?

26:15.110 --> 26:16.960
Elder Helian, you don't need to worry.

26:16.960 --> 26:19.240
I have led troops to quell the rebellion
in the city,

26:19.240 --> 26:21.300
and captured more than 2,000 rebels.

26:22.480 --> 26:23.810
Then I can rest assured.

26:24.160 --> 26:25.110
Such a relief.

26:25.440 --> 26:26.200
Since that's the case,

26:26.200 --> 26:27.590
thank you for your hard work,
General Huan.

26:27.590 --> 26:28.450
Please go back.

26:29.030 --> 26:31.000
If the Lanchuan Tribe alone

26:31.000 --> 26:32.110
could have successfully rebelled,

26:32.110 --> 26:35.710
then it must have been Heaven's will
that Great Yan be destroyed.

26:38.790 --> 26:39.590
Wait.

26:40.920 --> 26:42.780
The Lanchuan Tribe has rebelled.

26:43.400 --> 26:45.270
Instead of going to the Lanchuan Tribe
to arrest the rebels,

26:45.270 --> 26:47.670
what are you doing here
in the Helian Tribe?

26:50.200 --> 26:51.830
Among these 2,000 rebels,

26:52.310 --> 26:54.240
300 are from the Helian Tribe.

26:55.110 --> 26:55.790
Guards!

27:00.110 --> 27:01.750
Elder Helian has just woken up.

27:01.750 --> 27:04.150
I'm afraid he isn't seeing things clearly.

27:04.640 --> 27:05.640
Consort Helian,

27:06.550 --> 27:09.270
do you recognize these two rebels?

27:19.350 --> 27:20.270
These two

27:20.640 --> 27:22.900
are my brother's trusted subordinates.

27:23.110 --> 27:24.510
They have followed him for many years.

27:24.510 --> 27:25.310
Ling,

27:26.200 --> 27:27.940
this is a grave crime of rebellion.

27:27.940 --> 27:29.110
You must not talk nonsense.

27:29.110 --> 27:31.710
Our Helian Tribe
is related to the royal family

27:31.750 --> 27:33.350
and already holds noble status
with everything we need.

27:33.350 --> 27:34.410
Why would we rebel?

27:38.680 --> 27:39.640
I remember now.

27:41.000 --> 27:42.110
The day before yesterday,

27:42.110 --> 27:43.640
Elder Lanchuan said

27:44.000 --> 27:45.480
he wanted to go winter hunting
in the mountains.

27:45.480 --> 27:46.640
Because he didn't have enough men,

27:46.640 --> 27:48.170
I lent him these few people.

27:49.350 --> 27:50.350
That old bastard.

27:51.270 --> 27:52.960
He actually dared to rebel?

27:52.980 --> 27:54.840
Winter hunting in the mountains?

27:55.270 --> 27:57.030
Then what about the 1,000 Helian cavalry

27:57.030 --> 27:58.550
my men intercepted in Wuxian

27:58.550 --> 27:59.750
outside the Capital?

28:00.350 --> 28:04.080
How many troops did Elder Lanchuan want
to take for winter hunting?

28:05.150 --> 28:07.190
What does it matter to me?

28:09.070 --> 28:09.720
It's her!

28:10.790 --> 28:13.790
She must have been the one
plotting behind the scenes.

28:14.550 --> 28:16.410
Ask everyone in the Helian Tribe.

28:16.440 --> 28:18.370
Ever since she became the Consort,

28:18.480 --> 28:19.510
no one in the Helian Tribe

28:19.510 --> 28:20.960
has taken me seriously.

28:21.350 --> 28:22.110
And now?

28:22.480 --> 28:24.110
Something has happened
to the Helian family,

28:24.110 --> 28:25.720
and now you all come to ask me.

28:26.640 --> 28:29.160
Why don't you ask the real leader?

28:30.240 --> 28:31.100
Say something!

28:31.270 --> 28:32.130
Say something!

28:34.400 --> 28:36.000
Since Elder Helian won't admit it,

28:36.000 --> 28:38.440
it must be that these people have secretly
colluded with the rebels.

28:38.440 --> 28:39.830
According to the laws of Great Yan,

28:39.830 --> 28:41.000
rebels

28:41.030 --> 28:42.790
and their entire clan must be executed!

28:42.790 --> 28:44.120
General Huan, spare me!

28:44.270 --> 28:45.470
It was Master Helian.

28:45.880 --> 28:47.200
He told us to follow

28:47.270 --> 28:48.930
the orders of Elder Lanchuan.

28:49.270 --> 28:50.470
How dare you frame me!

28:50.550 --> 28:51.750
You... I...

29:00.680 --> 29:01.270
Ling,

29:01.680 --> 29:02.400
save me.

29:02.720 --> 29:03.580
I was deceived.

29:03.680 --> 29:05.510
I was deceived by Elder Lanchuan.

29:05.510 --> 29:06.570
I was really wrong.

29:07.070 --> 29:08.680
Save me just this last time.

29:08.920 --> 29:09.790
Save me, Ling.

29:10.000 --> 29:11.790
Great Yan has its own laws.

29:12.920 --> 29:13.720
General Huan,

29:14.920 --> 29:16.510
I am just a consort.

29:17.110 --> 29:18.400
Who dares to kill me?

29:18.420 --> 29:20.420
I am the master of the Helian family!

29:25.030 --> 29:26.110
Helian Ling!

29:26.590 --> 29:28.520
You are not just Yan Xun's Consort.

29:28.960 --> 29:30.760
You are one of the Helian family.

29:31.110 --> 29:32.550
You are my sister!

29:32.920 --> 29:33.550
Today,

29:33.960 --> 29:35.640
if you let them kill me,

29:36.200 --> 29:37.070
your hands

29:37.480 --> 29:40.080
will be stained
with your own brother's blood!

29:40.240 --> 29:42.680
And you will be the one
who destroys the Helian family!

29:42.680 --> 29:44.940
You will be a sinner to the Helian family!

29:50.640 --> 29:52.370
Besides you, the Helian family

29:52.790 --> 29:54.160
has 4 younger brothers.

29:55.350 --> 29:56.830
Although they are young,

29:57.680 --> 29:59.010
if they are raised well,

29:59.110 --> 30:01.440
they can surely take on
the role of Master.

30:02.200 --> 30:03.310
If they cannot,

30:04.030 --> 30:05.270
there are still 6 girls.

30:05.270 --> 30:07.130
They are all of the same clan as us.

30:07.730 --> 30:10.390
Every one of them
has better character than you.

30:10.960 --> 30:13.290
They might also take on
the role of Master.

30:13.680 --> 30:15.590
The king's law applies
not only to subordinates,

30:15.590 --> 30:16.850
but also to superiors.

30:17.030 --> 30:17.830
General Huan,

30:19.440 --> 30:22.400
let the punishment fit the crime.

30:25.790 --> 30:28.450
You will always be a sinner
to the Helian family!

30:46.480 --> 30:48.080
Since you dared to come back,

30:48.350 --> 30:50.550
you must have prepared an explanation.

30:52.160 --> 30:52.830
Speak.

30:53.110 --> 30:54.200
Let me hear

30:55.160 --> 30:56.440
what excuses you have

30:57.110 --> 30:58.640
to get yourself out of this.

30:59.310 --> 31:01.440
I didn't plan to get myself out of this.

31:01.550 --> 31:04.310
Ever since I fell into the frozen lake
during the battle at Meilin Pass,

31:04.310 --> 31:05.830
I have been a dead man.

31:06.160 --> 31:08.350
I was lucky enough to be saved
by the people of Ximeng,

31:08.350 --> 31:09.440
but I was forced

31:09.440 --> 31:11.240
to take Ximeng's deadly poison,

31:11.680 --> 31:14.340
and have been controlled
like a walking corpse,

31:14.750 --> 31:17.110
able to live only in the shadows.

31:21.590 --> 31:24.000
This was left to me by my grandfather
before he passed away.

31:24.000 --> 31:25.400
I have failed Great Yong.

31:25.550 --> 31:27.640
I am no longer fit
for this great responsibility.

31:27.640 --> 31:30.440
Your Majesty, please take back this seal

31:30.920 --> 31:32.850
and punish me according to the law.

31:51.950 --> 31:55.060
Back then, that old man Zhuge,

31:55.350 --> 31:58.160
in order to make me believe
you were already dead,

31:59.110 --> 32:00.000
drank

32:00.240 --> 32:03.440
poisoned wine
that destroyed all his martial arts skills

32:03.640 --> 32:04.790
as atonement.

32:05.830 --> 32:08.200
Since you yourself said you're guilty...

32:27.160 --> 32:28.400
I know I am guilty,

32:29.200 --> 32:31.660
and I am willing
to drink this poisoned wine.

32:40.960 --> 32:42.440
But I have one request.

32:42.920 --> 32:44.980
I hope you can grant it, Your Majesty.

32:46.200 --> 32:46.720
I know that

32:46.720 --> 32:48.920
during my absence from Qingshan Manor,

32:49.000 --> 32:50.480
Lord Muhe Lie of the Muhe family

32:50.480 --> 32:53.070
has trained a group of loyal men
for Your Majesty

32:53.070 --> 32:55.350
who are skilled in assassination
and intelligence gathering.

32:55.350 --> 32:57.350
Qingshan Manor has had no successor
in recent years.

32:57.350 --> 32:59.000
My grandfather has passed away.

32:59.000 --> 33:00.070
I lack both virtue and ability

33:00.070 --> 33:01.160
and am a criminal.

33:01.350 --> 33:03.350
I can no longer bear
such heavy responsibilities.

33:03.350 --> 33:05.240
Your Majesty, please issue an edict

33:05.240 --> 33:06.680
to disband Qingshan Manor

33:06.680 --> 33:09.510
and let its spies retire to their homes

33:09.790 --> 33:11.110
to spend the rest of their lives in peace.

33:11.110 --> 33:12.440
Do you want me

33:13.310 --> 33:14.750
to abolish Qingshan Manor?

33:14.750 --> 33:15.200
Yes.

33:20.270 --> 33:21.110
Zhuge Yue,

33:21.790 --> 33:23.000
let me tell you.

33:24.160 --> 33:26.020
Qingshan Manor can be abolished,

33:26.510 --> 33:28.110
but none of its people

33:28.830 --> 33:31.240
will be allowed to leave alive.

33:33.480 --> 33:35.210
Please don't be angry, Father.

33:38.030 --> 33:39.750
I have a good idea.

33:39.830 --> 33:40.480
Yang?

33:40.880 --> 33:42.210
What are you doing here?

33:54.240 --> 33:55.070
Yang,

33:55.680 --> 33:57.350
don't mess around.

33:57.920 --> 33:58.640
Father,

34:02.830 --> 34:05.440
Young Master Zhuge is not only capable,

34:05.880 --> 34:07.830
surviving death time and again,

34:08.710 --> 34:10.480
but also skilled in governing the country.

34:10.480 --> 34:12.320
Even when his own life is at stake,

34:12.320 --> 34:15.070
he still tries to find a way out
for his subordinates.

34:15.070 --> 34:16.330
Since that's the case,

34:17.070 --> 34:19.150
Father, you might as well grant his wish.

34:19.150 --> 34:20.510
What do you mean by that?

34:23.000 --> 34:23.880
Bring him in!

34:35.070 --> 34:35.800
Shiyi!

34:37.760 --> 34:38.690
Young Master...

34:40.030 --> 34:40.670
Shiyi!

34:42.230 --> 34:43.360
Young Master Zhuge,

34:43.400 --> 34:45.460
you know the rules of Qingshan Manor.

34:45.840 --> 34:47.480
Once you join, you can never leave.

34:47.480 --> 34:50.110
But your willingness
to risk your life for them

34:50.360 --> 34:52.800
truly moved me.

34:54.070 --> 34:54.960
How about this?

34:55.219 --> 34:57.780
Let him drink this poisoned wine
as an apology

34:58.400 --> 34:59.260
on your behalf,

34:59.710 --> 35:01.640
and I will plead with Father for you

35:02.110 --> 35:04.970
to let all these people
from Qingshan Manor retire.

35:05.440 --> 35:06.300
What do you say?

35:10.760 --> 35:11.400
Shiyi!

35:12.360 --> 35:13.230
Shiyi, don't!

35:15.480 --> 35:16.340
What do you say?

35:18.320 --> 35:19.070
Shiyi!

35:19.790 --> 35:23.250
Are you willing to drink this cup of wine
for your Young Master?

35:24.590 --> 35:26.030
Yue Shiyi, no!

35:26.630 --> 35:27.430
Young Master,

35:28.280 --> 35:30.360
you are a man destined for great things.

35:30.360 --> 35:31.590
I hope you won't think

35:31.590 --> 35:33.070
that I'm useless

35:33.140 --> 35:34.840
and will still let me keep following you.

35:34.840 --> 35:36.190
Yue Shiyi, no!

35:36.480 --> 35:36.920
Don't!

35:36.920 --> 35:38.380
Give it to me! Give it to me!

35:44.110 --> 35:46.570
What a deep bond
between master and servant.

35:46.960 --> 35:48.150
I'm so touched.

35:48.440 --> 35:49.500
But this cup of wine

35:49.710 --> 35:51.320
is different from the one

35:51.550 --> 35:52.750
old Master Zhuge had.

35:52.920 --> 35:55.180
It is a rare poison I specially obtained.

35:55.590 --> 35:56.650
After drinking it,

35:56.760 --> 35:59.590
you will feel as if venomous insects
are biting through your veins,

35:59.590 --> 36:01.990
and you will scream
until your last breath.

36:02.030 --> 36:03.160
Young Master Zhuge,

36:03.440 --> 36:04.840
the stakes have changed.

36:05.110 --> 36:05.760
You,

36:07.510 --> 36:08.280
or him—

36:11.800 --> 36:13.030
how will you choose?

36:14.630 --> 36:15.360
I'll drink it!

36:15.360 --> 36:15.920
Shiyi!

36:15.920 --> 36:16.400
I'll drink it!

36:16.400 --> 36:17.150
Yue Shiyi!

36:17.230 --> 36:18.070
I'll drink it!

36:18.320 --> 36:19.000
Your Majesty!

36:19.000 --> 36:20.950
I've heard
that you dote on the Thirteenth Prince

36:20.950 --> 36:22.570
and intend to entrust him with

36:22.570 --> 36:24.400
the great responsibility of Great Yong.

36:24.400 --> 36:25.550
In my opinion,

36:26.000 --> 36:29.190
you should teach him
how to govern a country properly,

36:29.190 --> 36:32.880
rather than treating the slaughter
of loyal subjects as child's play!

36:32.880 --> 36:33.710
Zhuge Yue,

36:34.510 --> 36:36.640
I hate the way you always look the most.

36:37.110 --> 36:38.510
Now I want to see whether,

36:39.480 --> 36:41.550
after you drink this cup of poisoned wine,

36:41.550 --> 36:44.510
you can still remain
as calm as you are now.

37:07.150 --> 37:09.000
Shiyi!

37:20.110 --> 37:20.840
Shiyi...

37:21.960 --> 37:22.590
Enough.

37:24.630 --> 37:25.430
Your Majesty,

37:26.150 --> 37:28.360
I have drunk the poisoned wine
for Young Master.

37:28.360 --> 37:29.890
Your word is as good as gold.

37:30.760 --> 37:33.090
Please let everyone in Qingshan Manor go.

37:51.510 --> 37:52.280
Zhuge Yue,

37:52.800 --> 37:55.510
for the sake of the late Zhuge Muqing,

37:55.710 --> 37:57.310
I'll let bygones be bygones.

37:57.670 --> 37:59.590
But if you don't know what's good for you,

37:59.590 --> 38:00.110
I...

38:01.000 --> 38:02.660
will destroy Qingshan Manor.

38:03.070 --> 38:04.800
Every one of your subordinates

38:06.630 --> 38:07.920
will be buried

38:09.110 --> 38:09.920
with it.

38:27.320 --> 38:28.160
Shiyi!

38:33.150 --> 38:33.840
Shiyi!

38:45.030 --> 38:46.880
In my next life,

38:50.000 --> 38:51.760
I will still follow you.

40:05.200 --> 40:11.520
[Qingshan Manor]

40:47.280 --> 40:48.080
Young Master.

40:51.320 --> 40:52.730
These are the Moon Guard tags

40:52.730 --> 40:55.520
of Yue Sheng, Yue Bo, and Yue Shijiu.

40:55.880 --> 40:57.760
They were taken away with Shiyi.

40:58.670 --> 41:02.070
The Thirteenth Prince
handed them over to the Muhe family...

41:02.230 --> 41:03.490
and let the Muhe family

41:03.710 --> 41:05.310
interrogate them about you.

41:06.190 --> 41:07.850
To avoid dragging you down...

41:10.110 --> 41:11.710
they all killed themselves.

41:27.000 --> 41:28.030
These tags

41:28.920 --> 41:31.230
were sent by the Muhe family.

41:33.000 --> 41:33.800
Young Master.

41:34.480 --> 41:37.480
The Muhe family has wanted to uproot
Qingshan Manor for a long time.

41:37.480 --> 41:39.920
Now that they have attached themselves
to Zhao Yang,

41:39.920 --> 41:43.280
they will definitely use him
to wipe us out.

41:43.280 --> 41:45.210
Everyone, don't lose your spirit!

41:45.230 --> 41:47.110
Now that the Young Master is back,

41:47.760 --> 41:50.220
he will definitely protect Qingshan Manor.

41:56.510 --> 41:57.310
Young Master.

41:59.440 --> 42:00.510
You know the rules.

42:00.960 --> 42:02.550
Yue Shiyi was your Moon Guard

42:02.550 --> 42:04.360
and also a spy from Qingshan Manor.

42:04.360 --> 42:05.150
His body...

42:06.480 --> 42:07.340
cannot be kept.

42:13.840 --> 42:15.640
I am the Chief of Qingshan Manor.

42:16.070 --> 42:18.920
I will handle Yue Shiyi's body personally.

43:36.630 --> 43:38.430
Lord Zhan came by during the day.

43:38.840 --> 43:41.300
He took the files
of Yue Shiyi and the others.

43:41.760 --> 43:43.090
Young Master, don't go!

43:44.030 --> 43:44.960
It's pointless.

43:46.280 --> 43:47.810
Once a spy of Qingshan Manor

43:47.880 --> 43:48.880
is convicted,

43:49.800 --> 43:52.200
none of their family members will survive.

43:53.400 --> 43:54.030
Do you know

43:54.840 --> 43:56.640
where Yue Shiyi's family lives?

43:56.760 --> 43:59.090
What was his real name
Where is his family?

43:59.630 --> 44:00.560
Young Master...

44:02.150 --> 44:03.030
It's too late.

44:04.440 --> 44:06.300
Lord Zhan has already been there.

44:06.590 --> 44:07.880
You can't save them.

44:39.960 --> 44:40.490
How is it?

44:40.760 --> 44:43.160
How does it feel
to be betrayed by everyone?

44:44.920 --> 44:45.630
So,

44:46.110 --> 44:48.190
this was all your plan.

44:50.070 --> 44:51.030
General Huan,

44:51.880 --> 44:53.680
are you making decisions for me?

44:53.760 --> 44:54.400
Helian!

44:56.580 --> 44:58.100
I have no way back,

44:59.050 --> 44:59.780
do I?
